    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/sheikhashadul/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_ARTICLE&editorId=607381796862034487&sectionId=607399029579449242)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7RcLGLINb_text","label":"gg7RcLGLINb_text","default":"<p>To achieve this type of skin transformation yourself...</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggn5LBBgigT_childItem_0","label":"ggn5LBBgigT_childItem_0","default":"<p>Adding more collagen</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggn5LBBgigT_childItem_1","label":"ggn5LBBgigT_childItem_1","default":"<p>Hydrating the skin</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggn5LBBgigT_childItem_2","label":"ggn5LBBgigT_childItem_2","default":"<p>Exfoliating dead cells</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggn5LBBgigT_childItem_3","label":"ggn5LBBgigT_childItem_3","default":"<p>Protecting from sun damage</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggn5LBBgigT_childItem_4","label":"ggn5LBBgigT_childItem_4","default":"<p>Plumping with hyaluronic acid<br>&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggpS471VD8v_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggpS471VD8v_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s7bx1bg.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQ_BbFw8ba_text","label":"ggQ_BbFw8ba_text","default":"<p>But none of these address the root cause – <strong>Progerin buildup in your skin cells.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggNFZtz7xf7_text","label":"ggNFZtz7xf7_text","default":"<p>In fact, when I looked closely at the research and compared it to my own clinical experience, I began to notice something remarkable.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg1nkIJFGDK_text","label":"gg1nkIJFGDK_text","default":"<p>You see, many skincare products actually contain ingredients that do nothing to address Progerin that’s building up in your skin with every passing year.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggS4QpCDhUg_text","label":"ggS4QpCDhUg_text","default":"<p>But when I studied the successful cases, I found something extraordinary...</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg1uEbD9KWU_text","label":"gg1uEbD9KWU_text","default":"<p><strong>Every effective anti-aging treatment contains specific compounds that seem to COUNTERACT the effects of Progerin.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggO2KT9aTLg_text","label":"ggO2KT9aTLg_text","default":"<p>Let me repeat this, because it's very important…</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQFl8PaoGp_text","label":"ggQFl8PaoGp_text","default":"<p>Aging skin occurs when Progerin builds up in our cells...but specific peptides exist that can help combat Progerin damage and actually help you maintain youthful skin.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggPj-4lNVeU_text","label":"ggPj-4lNVeU_text","default":"<p>That's right. While most anti-aging products just sit on the surface, certain compounds can penetrate deep into the skin to fight this aging protein.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqeGJPKoh2_text","label":"ggqeGJPKoh2_text","default":"<p>Even more amazing, it's not the ingredients themselves that do it...</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggI5SrfopBc_text","label":"ggI5SrfopBc_text","default":"<p>These peptides help your body's natural repair processes work better.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggU67xjylQm_text","label":"ggU67xjylQm_text","default":"<p><strong>And the \"hero\" of your skin's youth is an incredible compound called Progeline.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggn8jXbVAZH_text","label":"ggn8jXbVAZH_text","default":"<p>Progeline is a remarkable peptide. It's one of the most important age-fighting substances in dermatology.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggk8rF0ewNp_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggk8rF0ewNp_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s7img.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggXnhWZIYU-_text","label":"ggXnhWZIYU-_text","default":"<p>(That's the scientific name for it... but I like to<br>call this crucial anti-aging compound a \"skin youth factor.\")</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggi2cUQfYCu_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggi2cUQfYCu_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s7img.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggfHWDgQhXr_text","label":"ggfHWDgQhXr_text","default":"<p>In your skin, this superhero ingredient is<br>in charge of many things:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggH-IF72JEI_childItem_0","label":"ggH-IF72JEI_childItem_0","default":"<p>It helps <strong>REDUCE </strong>existing Progerin levels</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggH-IF72JEI_childItem_1","label":"ggH-IF72JEI_childItem_1","default":"<p>It supports <strong>NATURAL </strong>collagen production</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggH-IF72JEI_childItem_2","label":"ggH-IF72JEI_childItem_2","default":"<p>It <strong>SUPPORTS </strong>skin firmness and elasticity</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggH-IF72JEI_childItem_3","label":"ggH-IF72JEI_childItem_3","default":"<p>It <strong>HELPS </strong>skin cells function optimally</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggH-IF72JEI_childItem_4","label":"ggH-IF72JEI_childItem_4","default":"<p>Most importantly, it helps <strong>PROTECT </strong>your skin against future aging</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggdcORxlzMl_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggdcORxlzMl_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s7bx2bg_852cf72e-2a5c-484b-a5e4-31e1f2bc42d1.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggfMfvQvs78_text","label":"ggfMfvQvs78_text","default":"<p>But most powerful of all... Progeline can actually strengthen your skin's repair processes.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggXOYUIFEV9_text","label":"ggXOYUIFEV9_text","default":"<p>Research shows it does this by reducing Progerin levels by an astonishing 22%!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_sKqDZmEM_text","label":"gg_sKqDZmEM_text","default":"<p>That’s like rolling back the clock on your skin by 7-8 years!</p>"}],
